### IVCF Patient API Tests

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8000/api/v1

### Create IVCF Patient
POST {{baseUrl}}/ivcf-patients/
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nome_completo": "Maria Silva Santos",
  "cpf": "12345678901",
  "idade": 72,
  "telefone": "41999999999",
  "bairro": "Centro",
  "unidade_saude_id": 1,
  "data_cadastro": "2024-01-15"
}

